title: Stimulus, Keystone XL, Rep. Bryan Steil
itunes:title: Stimulus, Keystone XL, Rep. Bryan Steil
description:
Host: Jeanne Sheehan Zaino, Bloomberg contributor and Iona College Professor. Guests: Rick Davis, Partner at Stone Court Capital, former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, Roger Fisk, Democratic Strategist and Principal of New Day Strategy, and Rep. Bryan Steil, a Republican representing Wisconsin’s 1st Congressional District.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
